                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p>be able to identify equations representing sec-hyperbolas.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p>be able to find the center, vertices, foci, and asymptotes of a hyperbola and sketch the hyperbola.</p>
                    </li>
